      "description": "Looking for a rewarding weekend project? This vehicle is ready for some serious TLC and a new lease on life! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a fantastic foundation for a dedicated restorer. It's an affordable way to get your hands on a car with great potential once you put in the effort!",
