    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
