    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the S54 naturally aspirated straight-six, featuring a flawlessly maintained valvetrain and recently recalibrated VANOS system. The 3.2L powerplant breathes through six individual throttle bodies, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response that remains unmatched. This example features the sought-after 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in showroom state, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous mechanical stewardship.",
      "price": 46500.0,
