    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior retains its original showroom luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in untouched condition; the premium leather still carries its factory aroma, and the bolsters show zero signs of wear or compression. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Features include the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and unused factory floor mats. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a time-capsule vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 43900.0,
